\varepsilon>0,~p\in\mathbb R^2
B_\delta(p,\varepsilon)=\begin{cases} \{ p \} & \text{if }p\ne0,\; d(p,0)\ge\varepsilon\\ B_d(0,\varepsilon-d(p,0))\cup\{p\} & \text{if }p\ne0,\;d(p,0)<\varepsilon\\ B_d(0,\varepsilon) & \text{if }p=0 \end{cases}
